senselogic.sitevision.api.user

Interface UserFactory


  • @Requireable(value="UserFactory")
public interface UserFactory
    Factory for creating user-related instances.

    An instance of the Sitevision class implementing this interface can be obtained via Utils.getUserFactory(). See Utils for how to obtain an instance of the Utils interface.

    Since:
    Sitevision 3.6
